Maintainer: Dr. Steven Mack <Steven.Mack@ucsf.edu>
Description: A toolkit for the analysis and management of Human Leukocyte Antigen (HLA) gene data. Included functions perform extraction of reference data from the ANHIG/IMGTHLA GitHub repo, Genotype List (GL) String validation, conversions between UNIFORMAT and GL String Code (GLSC) formats, HLA allele and GLSC translation across IPT-IMGT/HLA Database release versions, customized, multi-position sequence searches of HLA nucleotide and peptide alignments, and allele-name trimming across nomenclature epochs. The associated HLAtools.data package includes alignments of amino acid, cDNA, and gDNA sequences for HLA genes..
